Description:
28th Oct- 5th Nov

Client- Digvijay is one of the main branch manager or  you can say he is looking after the main establishment of the gym setup. He has already seen InBody in different gyms in pune and also used them . 

Ayan- When I called him he told that yes they are coming up with a new gym but he is not sure that when it will start. So I requested him that if he can make an arrangement to meet the owner of the gym.

Client- Had a word with is owner and asked to come for a demo and meeting.

Ayan- arrange demo and meeting by next week . The demo and the meeting will be done between 9th Nov- 15th Nov

Brief about the company - Its a school who is coming up with a in-house gym setup in the school , so MrPranav Pillai has already used our machine in some of the gym so he is looking to showcase and refer our machine to his management and try to push for it into the gym
Ayan- I had a meeting with him regarding how our machine can be helpfull for their students, different types of machine etc. and also requested for a demo schedule .
Pranav- He has told me that he will confirm from the management and will update me the same.

Brief- The company is into renting services of It equipement, Kitchen equipement, Fitness equipement to big hotels, hospitals and corporates.
Ayan- I had a meeting with him regarding our different models and how he can push such all models into the their gym renting offers.
Jagminder- He has already used the InBody machine in multifit and also he knows about the machine. Now he wants to buy our machine and give it to big hotels or hospitals on a renting basis. 
Ayan - I have asked him to work together and cater to the hotel & Hospital industry, so that it can be captured on a short period.
Jagminder - He was interested and he wants to see and work how it can be possible.
Ayan- I have asked him that I will share the dealers document with him. As it is taking little time for approval or changes from the management.

So Dr.Vipul is the director of ISST institute in Pune which is into sports management, fitness management etc undergrad and post graduation college.
Ayan- My aim for connecting is to sale one of our machine into their PG  nutrition course and PG fitness course.
